text: Wesley Koolhof and Matwé Middelkoop were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Julian Knowle and Igor Zelenay won the title after defeating Facundo Argüello and Julio Peralta 6–4, 7–5 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Advantage Cars Prague Open - Men's Doubles Category:Advantage Cars Prague Open
